    <profile name="Nemesis Force Weapon (Justicar/Terminator/Brother-Captain)" typeId="b399-8a1b-bf0b-c5b7" typeName="Weapon" hidden="false" id="8c2f-c8de-89be-f667">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Range" typeId="deb8-131d-bdcf-1376">Melee</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="S" typeId="24d8-2110-08fa-d844">User +2</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="AP" typeId="25ce-028f-0aae-2855">2</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="Type" typeId="d3f6-19e8-ac9e-ae13">Melee</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="Abilities" typeId="492d-1f80-b777-26f2">Ignores the target Armor Save (Sv) (but not Invulnerable Save). 


When specified, grants a bonus to S or Wounds on a fixed value regardless of target Toughness (T).</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile name="Nemesis Force Weapon (Grand Master)" typeId="b399-8a1b-bf0b-c5b7" typeName="Weapon" hidden="false" id="cb23-151b-1e1b-eae2">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Range" typeId="deb8-131d-bdcf-1376">Melee</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="S" typeId="24d8-2110-08fa-d844">User +2</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="AP" typeId="25ce-028f-0aae-2855">2</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="Type" typeId="d3f6-19e8-ac9e-ae13">Melee</characteristic>
        <characteristic name="Abilities" typeId="492d-1f80-b777-26f2">Ignores the target Armor Save (Sv) (but not Invulnerable Save). 


When specified, grants a bonus to S or Wounds on a fixed value regardless of target Toughness (T).


Rolls To-Hit and To-Wound as normal, allowing any Invulnerable Save. 




For any Wound that wasn’t Saved (Sv), the model equipped with the Force Weapon makes a Psychic Test. 




On success the target suffers Instant Death regardless of remaining Wounds. 




Has no effect against targets without Wounds such as Vehicles.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
